OL,4,Cbusiness 'obliterated' by fire
OL,6,FThe owner of a popular coffee roastery
OL,7,Fsays he is devastated after losing
OL,8,Fdecades of hard work in minutes, when
OL,9,Ftheir family business went up in
OL,10,Fflames.
OL,12,FHormozi Coffee, in Sittingbourne,
OL,13,FKent, has been running for 25 years,
OL,14,Fspanning two generations.
OL,16,FTheir main unit, at Precision 4
OL,17,FBusiness Park, which they have
OL,18,Foccupied since 2018, was destroyed in
OL,19,Fa fire which broke out at around
OL,20,F11.50am on Friday (25 April).
