OL,6,FFlames could be seen coming out of the
OL,7,Fwindows and the roof.
OL,9,FAround 100 firefighters were sent to
OL,10,Fthe scene, which took them more than
OL,11,F24 hours to completely extinguish.
OL,13,FEmergency crews left the following
OL,14,Fday, just after 1.15pm. The cause of
OL,15,Fthe fire is under investigation.
OL,17,FRubin Hormozi said coffee stock and
OL,18,Fmachinery was lost, with the fire
OL,19,Fresulting in damage running to tens of
OL,20,Fthousands of pounds.
