OL,6,FNeighbours, Mid-Kent Mezzanine, which
OL,7,Fwas also damaged in the fire, have
OL,8,Fbeen supporting the Hormozi family and
OL,9,Fhelped them set up a fundraiser.
OL,11,FThe GoFundMe page, set up on Saturday
OL,12,F(26 April), has raised more than
OL,13,F#4,000, to help Rubin rebuild his
OL,14,Ffamily's business.
OL,16,FDaniel Mulholland, Director of Mid-
OL,17,FKent Mezzanine said: "The problem is
OL,18,Fthe insurance isn't going to cover
OL,19,Feverything anyway. At the minute
OL,20,Fthey're in limbo because they've got
OL,21,Fno support from anybody.
