OL,6,F"With what they do, they've got to be
OL,7,Foperating daily. They've lost
OL,8,Feverything. Their unit is completely
OL,9,Fobliterated, they've got nothing.
OL,11,F"They're really nice guys, everybody
OL,12,Floves the Hormozis. They always help
OL,13,Feverybody out, everything you need,
OL,14,Fyou can always go to them and rely on
OL,15,Fthem, so to help them out now, when
OL,16,Fthey're in their time of need, is what
OL,17,Feverybody should be aiming for."
